    "description": "《循环圈:保卫战》是一款循环圈类型的塔防游戏，在数十座防御塔中通过组合所创建的防御塔羁绊，来使防御塔能力获得提升，解锁更多的能力，然后不断挑战更强大的敌人让防御塔变得更加强大！总之你做所的一切都是为了让防御塔更加强大，来击败所有敌人！<br><br><i>击败最终BOSS！获得游戏胜利！</i><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏玩法</h2><br>在怪物达到数量上限之前，消灭他们，只要怪物没有达到数量上限，那么他们就会围绕着地图行走，直至他们的灭亡！<br>而您要做的，就是配置强大的防御塔火力网，通过配置羁绊与九个玩家天赋，组合出最为强大的阵容！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >召唤防御塔</h2>﻿<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100330/extras/6d2a238ca84d7e01436328cdd6eb5517.poster.avif?t=1722426617\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100330/extras/6d2a238ca84d7e01436328cdd6eb5517.webm?t=1722426617\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100330/extras/6d2a238ca84d7e01436328cdd6eb5517.mp4?t=1722426617\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>在购买了防御塔之后可以点击背包中防御塔进行召唤<br>﻿<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >组合羁绊</h2>﻿<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100330/extras/902366595091886c99cb51905299b302.poster.avif?t=1722426617\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100330/extras/902366595091886c99cb51905299b302.webm?t=1722426617\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100330/extras/902366595091886c99cb51905299b302.mp4?t=1722426617\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>每个防御塔都带有羁绊，通过组合羁绊来获得属性的提升<br>﻿<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >防御塔升星</h2>﻿<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100330/extras/00fedbf490bbc5a9c634f4a8929dce77.poster.avif?t=1722426617\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100330/extras/00fedbf490bbc5a9c634f4a8929dce77.webm?t=1722426617\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100330/extras/00fedbf490bbc5a9c634f4a8929dce77.mp4?t=1722426617\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>拥有3座相同的防御塔，就会升级为下一星级的防御塔<br>﻿<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >装备合成</h2>﻿<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100330/extras/b6035235ddb7650331cbb172cfced2ae.poster.avif?t=1722426617\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100330/extras/b6035235ddb7650331cbb172cfced2ae.webm?t=1722426617\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3100330/extras/b6035235ddb7650331cbb172cfced2ae.mp4?t=1722426617\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>在游戏中根据装备的介绍来合成更强大的装备",
